{"word":"H2287 - חָגַג - châgag - khaw-gag' - Celebrate","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חָגַג</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>châgag"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khaw-gag'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Celebrate"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஆசரி, ஆடு, தடுமாறு, பண்டிகைஆசரி, பண்டிகை கொண்டாடு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to hold a feast, to hold a festival, to make a pilgrimage, to keep a pilgrim - feast, to celebrate, to dance, to stagger (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to keep a pilgrim - feast"},{"paragraph":"2) to reel"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root (compare <a href=\"#/H2283 - חָגָא - châgâʼ - khaw-gaw'/2283\">H2283</a>, <a href=\"#/H2328 - חוּג - chûwg - khoog/2328\">H2328</a>); properly to move in a <i>circle</i>, that is, (specifically) to <i>march</i> in a sacred procession, to <i>observe</i> a festival; by implication to <i>be giddy: - </i>celebrate, dance, (keep, hold) a (solemn) feast (holiday), reel to and fro."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2282 - חַג - chag - khag/2282\">H2282</a>, <a href=\"#/H2283 - חָגָא - châgâʼ - khaw-gaw'/2283\">H2283</a>, <a href=\"#/H2287 - חָגַג - châgag - khaw-gag'/2287\">H2287</a>, <a href=\"#/H2291 - חַגִּי - Chaggîy - khag-ghee'/2291\">H2291</a>, <a href=\"#/H2292 - חַגַּי - Chaggay - khag-gah'-ee/2292\">H2292</a>, <a href=\"#/H2293 - חַגִּיָּה - Chaggîyâh - khag-ghee-yaw'/2293\">H2293</a>, <a href=\"#/H2294 - חַגִּית - Chaggîyth - khag-gheeth'/2294\">H2294</a>"}]}